room_title: Escape room "Lockbuster Video" by Escape 605 in Sioux Falls
room_description: It’s December 1996 and you and your friends are returning a recent video rental to your local Lockbuster Video. Unfortunately, the employees have already closed for the night and went out the back entrance, locking you in. You must maneuver your way down memory lane through the store, locate the fuse panel to deactivate the alarm and unlock the exit door, all before local security comes back through, to succeed at this adventure. Remember the 90’s? You will after this!
